# The only Dockerfile in this repo is website/Dockerfile, which builds the Astro
# site from the repo-root build context (Railway default). Narrow that context to
# website/ so the multi-GB monorepo (crates, pyodide wasm, etc.) is never sent to
# the builder. If another Dockerfile is added that needs more, revisit this.
*
!website
website/node_modules
website/dist
website/.astro
